{"tid":659082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果甲由既驚嚇程度係10分，天牛值幾多分","createTime":"2018-05-09T13:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T16:09:15.000Z","uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32ea75875b350cfd8c4b1cc017bbbd3701487930","tid":659082,"uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"樣:<br />\n甲由(2/2)<br />\n唔洗講 好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n天牛(1.5/2)<br />\n冇甲由咁樣衰 但好似樣 一飛入來會嚇親<br />\n知道唔係甲由個心^_^會定啲<br />\n<br />\n體型:<br />\n甲由(4/4)<br />\n無論幾大隻都好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n天牛(2/4)<br />\n普遍黎講細隻過識飛甲由(好似係<br />\n但對我黎講都好大隻<br />\n<br />\n行動率:<br />\n甲由(2/2)<br />\n<br />\n天牛(2/2)<br />\n兩隻都亂鳩咁黎 飛黎飛去<br />\n我愛飛蛾<br />\n<br />\n速度:<br />\n甲由(2/2)<br />\n好撚快<br />\n<br />\n天牛(0.5/2)<br />\n除非你太慢 如果唔係揾個兜 應該都可以蓋住佢<br />\n但唔排除失手 所以0.5<br />\n<br />\n特別事項<br />\n但天牛條友成日企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跌落去嗰下個心離一離 <br />\n同埋日日沖涼都見到佢 加返2分<br />\n<br />\n我比8分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197a489aff79d45e7e861e44dfa7a5293bd21d4d","tid":659082,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"11分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b188cf2665191fe418ec43de20b57e1a596cb1e9","tid":659082,"uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197a489aff79d45e7e861e44dfa7a5293bd21d4d","tid":659082,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"11分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"咁甲由點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93f911206676d10d01aede4b5a22fdb3544daca","tid":659082,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b188cf2665191fe418ec43de20b57e1a596cb1e9","tid":659082,"uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197a489aff79d45e7e861e44dfa7a5293